creator: LG Electronics, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
LG Channels is LG's exclusive free streaming service, offering a wide selection of premium live and on-demand programming, including movies, TV shows, news, sports, children's' programs, and more, now available on-the-go on smartphones.

■ 100% free contents in the palm of your hand
Watch 100% free live channels anywhere you want! No subscriptions or credit card required. Just download the app and start watching!

■ Chromecast supported
Don't worry if you don't have LG webOS TV! You can enjoy LG Channels on big screens with Chromecast.

■ More to come!
We are working hard to bring you more contents. Stay tuned for more channels!

* Any feedback or suggestion? Feel free to contact us at lgch-support@lge.com.
descriptionShort: LG Channels is LG's exclusive streaming service.
